# Rebuild react-ui and Restart Dev Server After Every Change

After editing ANY file under `packages/react-ui/`, you MUST run ALL of these steps in order:

```bash
# 1. Rebuild the package
yarn workspace @mbari/react-ui build

# 2. Kill ALL stale processes on ports 3000 and 3002
lsof -ti :3000 | xargs kill -9 2>/dev/null
lsof -ti :3002 | xargs kill -9 2>/dev/null

# 3. Start a fresh dev server
cd /Users/salamy/workspace/Github/dash5/apps/lrauv-dash2 && yarn dev
```

**All three steps are mandatory every time.** Skipping any step means the browser serves stale compiled output and changes appear to have no effect.

Then commit and push once the server is confirmed ready (`✓ Ready` in output).
